{"tid":1749972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍城區G15影大頭","createTime":"2019-11-24T08:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T08:00:19.000Z","uid":58202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ede470457260df12a9c10f24bf0a5e7734cfa133","tid":1749972,"uid":58202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日9點幾鐘就走去排隊<br />\n大約9點10，有老人家問長者有無得<br />\n唔排隊入去<br />\n票站職員先係趕走左幾個<br />\n但就放左個拎拐杖既老人家入去fast track<br />\n<br />\n我大聲問 幾多歲可以行快線入去<br />\n票站職員話唔係睇幾歲<br />\n係身體狀況差就可以入去先<br />\n咁優惠既消息我聽到緊係大大聲宣傳<br />\n比各位老人家唔可咁辛苦慢慢排<br />\n<br />\n過左無耐圖中人就走埋黎影左我大頭<br />\n影大頭咁開心我緊係唔執輸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Y3NkV0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Y3NkV0.jpg&h=092591d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HofjWuo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHofjWuo.jpg&h=93fefc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MkwrBur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkwrBur.jpg&h=7255122c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/osHBYHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FosHBYHO.jpg&h=e07422b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1JYsBb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1JYsBb.jpg&h=a3002cef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XatmqnU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXatmqnU.jpg&h=be694a2e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}